the perfect match is a british comedy-drama television film written by mike &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and directed by nick hurran . it stars saskia reeves and con o'neill as bridget and phil , a couple whose marriage proposal is broadcast to football fans . it was first broadcast on the itv network on 6 september 1995 . the programme was not well received by critics but it was enough of a success for producers granada television to ask &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; for further ideas , leading to the commissioning of the long-running television series cold feet .